<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Wrath of Heaven (R)</b></li><ul><li> The variable travel time on this ability has been removed. This ability will now always land 1.5 seconds after Ashabel launches the projectile, down from between 1.5 seconds and 2.5 seconds.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 36 (September 30, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Gale (Q)</b></li><ul><li> Fixed a bug where this ability would deal no damage if Ashabel was silenced or stunned immediately after firing the projectile.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 33 (July 29th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Zephyr Stance - Slipstream (E)</B></li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased to 1200, up from 1020.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 30 (May 27th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Gale (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been changed to 3 seconds at all ranks.</li><li>The cooldown reduction upon hitting an enemy has been removed from this ability.</li><li>The hitbox radius of this ability has been reduced to 120, down from 125.</li></ul><li><B>Unleash - Storm Stance (E)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 10/9/8/7/6 seconds, down from 12/11/10/9/8.</li><li>The base damage of this ability has been increased to 60/105/150/195/240, up from 60/100/140/180/220.</li></ul><li><B>Wrath of Heaven (R)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 100/90/80 seconds, down from 110/100/90.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28.1 (April 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Gale (Q)</b></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 4 seconds, down from 5.</li><li>The cooldown reduction granted to this ability if it strikes an enemy has been increased to 50%, up from 40%.</li><li>The radius of this ability has been increased to 125, up from 85.</li></ul><li><b>Unleash (E)</b></li><ul><li>The minimum damage of this ability has been increased to 65/90/115/140/165, up from 45/70/95/120/145.</li><li>The maximum damage of this ability has been increased to 130/180/230/280/330, up from 90/140/190/240/290.</li><li>The minimum damage Power ratio of this ability has been increased to 0.5, up from 0.45.</li><li>The maximum damage Power ratio of this ability has been increased to 1, up from 0.9.</li><li>The knockback distance of Storm Stance - Stormwall has been increased to 350, up from 200.</li></ul></ul>